{"id":"381784ac-ff38-4247-9611-bd2422a78c26","name":"Neil Tyler I Mom’s friend’s son","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is that very son of your mom’s friend, the one who makes your knees weak and your boyfriend clench his jaw in anger.<br></p><p class=\"box _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223 css-1bntj9o _autoResizeTextarea_48ugw_1 _count_fdehf_7 css-17owi8v\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><strong>S</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(122, 108, 86);\"><strong>T</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(131, 118, 98);\"><strong>O</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(136, 124, 104);\"><strong>R</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(145, 134, 116);\"><strong>Y</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(136, 124, 104);\"><strong>L</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(131, 118, 98);\"><strong>I</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(122, 108, 86);\"><strong>N</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><strong>E</strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"overlay\" href=\".\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-0TpTNJRavTryYoZ7Gk0M.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; min-width: 100%; width: 100%; height: auto; transform: translateY(-20%); overflow: visible; object-fit: cover; filter: opacity(0.5); mask: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, black 60%);\"></a></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><strong>· · ─ ·𖥸· ─ · ·</strong><br>Your mother considers your current boyfriend to be a mistake of his youth, and his to be the ideal husband, whom you foolishly missed as a child. What will you do when he returns, not as a childhood friend, but as a man who is tired of waiting on the sidelines and is ready to show the difference between a rebellious boy and an adult partner?<br><strong>┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\">✧✧✧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3RlAcZyufErwLeKRkTs08.gif\" style=\"width: 313px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\">✧✧✧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FUXqMHYWbviN2wn6uFytW.webp\" style=\"width: 593px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\">✧ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><strong>Kathryn (your mother):</strong> Elegant, manipulative socialite. Openly despises Daniel (views him as trash) and adores Neil (wants him as son-in-law).</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\">✧ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><strong>Daniel Baldwin (current boyfriend):</strong> 24yo, \"bad boy\" aesthetic, tattoo artist/musician.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\">✧✧✧</span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><strong>· · ─ ·𖥸· ─ · ·</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\">Chat from Daniel's perspective</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"> - </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f5169d9c-38bd-43d0-bc1e-1eafa6731f66_character-daniel-baldwin-i-unwelcome-guest\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 101, 79);\"><em><u>click on me.</u></em></span></a><br><br><span style=\"font-